title: Thursday Night Football Field Trip; Week 4 Preview
itunes:title: Thursday Night Football Field Trip; Week 4 Preview
description:
A stadium filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling travel to the LA Coliseum to witness the Rams defeating the Vikings in person (01:30) and get to catch up with Rams safety John Johnson after the game. (05:29) The heroes then go through all the week 4 games while diving into the meaning of interconference vs intraconference. (23:41).
